      • parseUuidFrom

        public static android.os.ParcelUuid parseUuidFrom(byte[] uuidBytes)
        Parse UUID from bytes. The uuidBytes can represent a 16-bit, 32-bit or 128-bit UUID, but the returned UUID is always in 128-bit format. Note UUID is little endian in Bluetooth.
        参数:
        uuidBytes - Byte representation of uuid.
        返回:
        ParcelUuid parsed from bytes.
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If the uuidBytes cannot be parsed.
